    "Reason : 1 - The general height, scale and form of the proposed dwelling would be inappropriate for the proposal's location, and the resulting bulk and mass would serve to erode the character and appearance of the host site and surrounding area. The proposal is therefore contrary to policy CS14 of the Merton Core Planning Strategy (2011) and policy DMD2 of the Merton Sites and Policies Plan (2014).",
